<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="835bbb2f9d8fd926a7039d9f">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=7f91c182&authorId=0c0eaf1e44dbd14fb72e1c20&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/fd039245d688d43f0420e430711ed21b0ff43b62.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>热点说</strong>
<span>时事热点，尽情分享</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=835bbb2f9d8fd926a7039d9f&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/ac345982b2b7d0a25817206ac0ef76094a369a6e.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
与白居易有关的日子
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=835bbb2f9d8fd926a7039d9f&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
盛世大唐是最赋酒香诗意的时代。唐诗就像那时候的流行歌曲，一位位才华横溢的诗人则是彼时的超级大明星，其中最著名之一的就是白居易。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-12-25</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">2152</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="c305a5b02875616edb20b6ea">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=eae35e14&authorId=f484cb0e5420b0bd57ab5d21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b21bb051f8198618877f954646ed2e738bd4e63c.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>少读红楼</strong>
<span>文化自媒体，书评人</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=c305a5b02875616edb20b6ea&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/a08b87d6277f9e2fafbd49be1130e924b999f3f8.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
母亲节特辑丨历史上的三个“坏”母亲，专门拆散儿子姻缘
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=c305a5b02875616edb20b6ea&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
从另一个方面来讲，若非这几位“坏”母亲的“愚蠢”举动，也许我们看不到《孔雀东南飞》《长恨歌》《钗头凤》这样充满爱恨和悲痛的经典爱情诗作。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-05-13</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">1172</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="287cbd9a610678aeaaf4702a">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0576e634&authorId=cf1d6ae7ce4418d970d36d23&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d000baa1cd11728bd18d9a44c5fcc3cec3fd2c37.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>张苏君</strong>
<span>水浒职场点评人</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=287cbd9a610678aeaaf4702a&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/ac6eddc451da81cb863fbb0a5f66d0160824311f.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
诗王白居易：不要迷恋哥，哥只是传说
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=287cbd9a610678aeaaf4702a&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
唐朝诗人的生活质量，整体而言未必很高。洒脱自如的形象，可能是无所事事的无聊，忧国忧民的表相，
常常是底层生活的无奈。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-02-12</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">485</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="783743685171e82675f17d6e">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=783743685171e82675f17d6e&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/f2deb48f8c5494ee4e33f27323f5e0fe99257e43.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
诗仙白居易之风流：三年换一次情人和小三，还不放过好友之妾
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=783743685171e82675f17d6e&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
他的好友张愔之妾关盼盼原是徐州官妓，张愔病逝，关盼盼矢志守节，十年不下燕子楼。白居易看上关盼盼之后，极力去讨好，巴结，追求她，但关盼盼对张愔爱情忠贞，誓死不从。白居易追求无果，就指责她何不索性以死殉夫。性情贞烈的关盼盼在十天后绝食身亡，香销殒玉。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-16</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">421</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="625561342348ab4116010ee1">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=625561342348ab4116010ee1&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b999a9014c086e06888c74dc0e087bf40ad1cb05.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
大唐诗人白居易的女人们
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=625561342348ab4116010ee1&lemmaId=174330&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
白居易天生就是个心大，想得开的人。他很快就修正了自己的人生目标：由建功立业转到享受生活；很快就改变了自己的生活方式：由参与朝政改为泡妞纳妾；诗词作品也由关注现实生活，渐渐转入风花雪月，多写“江南好，风景旧曾谙。日出江花红胜火，春来江水绿如蓝。”这类享受玩味生活的作品。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-06-01</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">300</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
